org.eclipse.viatra.dse.guidance

Interface IOccurrenceVectorResolver


  • public interface IOccurrenceVectorResolver
    This interface defines a method which calculates an occurrence vector for the DSETransformationRules. Basically it is lower bound for the how many times they should be executed.
